params.sqlcmd: "SELECT T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.\\"PROJECT_CD\\" AS \\"PROJECT_CD\\",T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.\\"ESTIMATE_NO\\" AS \\"ESTIMATE_NO\\",T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.\\"DETAL_NO\\" AS \\"DETAL_NO\\",M_CUST.\\"CUST_NAME\\" AS \\"CUST_NAME\\" " +"FROM T_ESTIMATE_DETAL,M_CUST"
"SELECT " +" COMPANY_CD " +"FROM " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY " +"WHERE " +" CTRL_CD = 'SYSTEM'"
"SELECT " +" SYS_CLASS_CODE.CODE " +"FROM " +" SYS_CLASS_CODE " +"WHERE " +" SYS_CLASS_CODE.SYS_CLASS = ? " +" AND SYS_CLASS_CODE.CLASS_CODE = ?"
"SELECT " +" to_char(SYS_DATE_CTRL.BUSINESS_OPR_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') " +"FROM " +" SYS_DATE_CTRL " +"WHERE " +" SYS_DATE_CTRL.PLANT_CD = ?"
"SELECT " +" HOME_CUR_CD " +"FROM " +" SYS_HOME_CUR " +"WHERE " +" CTRL_CD = 'SYSTEM'"
"SELECT " +" VALUE " +"FROM " +" SYS_PARAMETER " +"WHERE " +" NAME = ?"
"SELECT " +" PROJECT_CD, " +" PROJECT_NAME, " +" CUST_CD, " +" PROJECT_STAT, " +" DLV_LOC_CD, " +" MODIFY_COUNT " +"FROM " +" T_PROJECT " +"WHERE " +" PROJECT_CD = ? " +" AND DEL_FLG = 0"
"UPDATE " +" T_PROJECT " +"SET " +" \\"PROJECT_STAT\\" = ? " +"WHERE " +" T_PROJECT.\\"PROJECT_CD\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" CUST_NAME, " +" CUR_CD, " +" M_CUST.\\"EXCH_TYP\\" AS \\"EXCH_TYP\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"TAX_APPLY_TYP\\" AS \\"TAX_APPLY_TYP\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"TAX_CD\\" AS \\"TAX_CD\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"TAX_CALC_TYP\\" AS \\"TAX_CALC_TYP\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"PARTIAL_SHIP_INST_FLG\\" AS \\"PARTIAL_SHIP_INST_FLG\\" " +"FROM " +" M_CUST " +"WHERE " +" COMPANY_CD = ? " +" AND CUST_CD = ?"
"SELECT " +" CUR_NAME, " +" CUR_UNIT, " +" DECIMAL_FIG " +"FROM " +" M_CUR " +"WHERE " +" CUR_CD = ?"

"SELECT " +" T_ESTIMATE.ES_USER_CD, " +" T_ESTIMATE.ES_ORG_CD, " +" T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.DETAL_NO, " +" T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.CUST_ITEM_CD, " +" T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.ESTIMATE_QTY, " +" T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.UNIT_CD, " +" T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.ESTIMATE_UNIT_PRICE, " +" T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.ESTIMATE_AMOUNT, " +" T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.ESTIMATE_TYPE, " +" T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.ITEM_NAME, " +" USER_MST.USER_NAME, " +" M_ORG.ORG_NAME " +"FROM " +" T_ESTIMATE, " +" T_ESTIMATE_DETAL, " +" ( " +" SELECT " +" T_ESTIMATE.PROJECT_CD AS PROJECT_CD, " +" MAX(T_ESTIMATE.ESTIMATE_NO) AS ESTIMATE_NO " +" FROM " +" T_ESTIMATE " +" WHERE " +" T_ESTIMATE.PROJECT_CD = ? " +" AND(0 = ? " +" OR T_ESTIMATE.ESTIMATE_NO = ?) " +" AND DEL_FLG = 0 " +" GROUP BY " +" T_ESTIMATE.PROJECT_CD " +" ) ESTIMATE, " +" USER_MST, " +" M_ORG " +"WHERE " +" T_ESTIMATE.PROJECT_CD = ESTIMATE.PROJECT_CD " +" AND T_ESTIMATE.ESTIMATE_NO = ESTIMATE.ESTIMATE_NO " +" AND T_ESTIMATE.PROJECT_CD = T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.PROJECT_CD " +" AND T_ESTIMATE.ESTIMATE_NO = T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.ESTIMATE_NO " +" AND T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.DEL_FLG = 0 " +" AND NOT EXISTS( " +" SELECT " +" 1 " +" FROM " +" T_PJ_ODR_ALC " +" WHERE " +" T_PJ_ODR_ALC.PROJECT_CD = T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.PROJECT_CD " +" AND T_PJ_ODR_ALC.ESTIMATE_NO = T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.ESTIMATE_NO " +" ) " +" AND T_ESTIMATE.ES_USER_CD = USER_MST.USER_CD(+) " +" AND T_ESTIMATE.ES_ORG_CD = M_ORG.ORG_CD(+) " +" AND M_ORG.COMPANY_CD(+) = ?"
"SELECT " +" PROJECT_CD " +"FROM " +" T_RLSD_PUCH_ODR " +"WHERE " +" PROJECT_CD = ?"

"SELECT " +" M_CUST_BASE.DLV_LOC_CD, " +" M_CUST_BASE.DLV_LOC_NAME, " +" M_CUST_BASE.TRANSPORT_LT, " +" M_CUST_BASE.\\"TRANSPORT_CD\\" AS \\"TRANSPORT_CD\\", " +" M_CUST_BASE.\\"TRANSPORT_TYP\\" AS \\"TRANSPORT_TYP\\", " +" M_CUST_BASE.\\"DEPO_WH_CD\\" AS \\"DEPO_WH_CD\\", " +" M_WH.\\"PLANT_CD\\" AS \\"SHIP_PLANT_CD\\" " +"FROM " +" M_CUST_BASE, " +" M_WH, " +" M_CUST " +"WHERE " +" M_CUST_BASE.SHIP_WH_CD = M_WH.WH_CD " +" AND M_CUST_BASE.CUST_CD = M_CUST.CUST_CD " +" AND M_CUST_BASE.COMPANY_CD = ? " +" AND M_CUST_BASE.CUST_CD = ? " +" AND M_CUST_BASE.DLV_LOC_CD = ?"

"SELECT " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.ITEM_CD, " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.DEPO_TYP, " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.CUST_ITEM_NAME, " +" M_ITEM.ITEM_NAME " +"FROM " +" M_ITEM_SPEC, " +" M_ITEM " +"WHERE " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.COMPANY_CD = ? " +" AND M_ITEM_SPEC.CUST_CD = ? " +" AND M_ITEM_SPEC.CUST_ITEM_CD = ? " +" AND M_ITEM_SPEC.ITEM_CD = M_ITEM.ITEM_CD"
"INSERT INTO " +" T_PJ_ODR_ALC(\\"PROJECT_CD\\", \\"ESTIMATE_NO\\", \\"DETAL_NO\\", \\"ODR_NO\\", \\"ESTIMATE_TYPE\\") " +"VALUES " +" (?, ?, ?, ?, ?)"

"SELECT " +" T_PJ_ODR_ALC.ESTIMATE_TYPE, " +" T_PJ_ODR_ALC.ODR_NO " +"FROM " +" T_PJ_ODR_ALC " +"WHERE " +" T_PJ_ODR_ALC.PROJECT_CD = ? " +" AND T_PJ_ODR_ALC.ESTIMATE_NO = ? " +" AND(? IS NOT NULL " +" AND T_PJ_ODR_ALC.DETAL_NO = ? " +" OR ? IS NULL)"
"DELETE FROM " +" T_PJ_ODR_ALC " +"WHERE " +" T_PJ_ODR_ALC.\\"PROJECT_CD\\" = ? " +" AND T_PJ_ODR_ALC.\\"ESTIMATE_NO\\" = ? " +" AND T_PJ_ODR_ALC.\\"DETAL_NO\\" = ?"

"INSERT INTO " +" T_ODR(\\"ODR_NO\\", \\"ODR_TYP\\", \\"ODR_CTL_NO\\", \\"CUST_ODR_NO\\", \\"CUST_CHRG_ORG_CD\\", \\"CUST_CHRG_PSN_CD\\", \\"ODR_ACPT_PSN_CD\\", \\"CURRNCY_CD\\", \\"EXCH_TYP\\", \\"DLV_LOC_CD\\", \\"DLV_LOC_NAME_KANJI\\", \\"ODR_UNIT_PRICE\\", \\"SPCL_PRICE_TYP\\", \\"DEPO_TYP\\", \\"DESINATED_DLV_DATE\\", \\"STD_DESINATED_RCV_DATE\\", \\"ODR_QTY\\", \\"REMAIN_UNCONFIRM_ODR_QTY\\", \\"CANCELED_UNCONFIRM_ODR_QTY\\", \\"UNIT_CD\\", \\"UNCONFIRM_ODR_BALANCE\\", \\"ODR_AMOUNT\\", \\"ODR_AMOUNT_EXCH_RATES\\", \\"ODR_CMPLT_FLG\\", \\"PART_NAME\\", \\"TRANSPORT_CD\\", \\"TRANSPORT_TYP\\", \\"TAX_APPLY_TYP\\", \\"TAX_CD\\", \\"TAX_CALC_TYP\\", \\"REMARKS\\", \\"ODR_ACPT_DATE\\", \\"SHIP_PLAN_REMAIN_QTY\\", \\"SHIP_PLAN_CMPLT_FLG\\", \\"UNCONFIRMED_ODR_EFF_OVR_FLG\\", \\"PARTIAL_SHIP_INST_FLG\\", \\"ENTRY_TYP\\", \\"DEL_FLG\\", \\"JOB_ODR_SET_FLG\\") " +"VALUES " +" (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, TO_DATE(?,'YYYY/MM/DD'), TO_DATE(?,'YYYY/MM/DD'), ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, TO_DATE(?,'YYYY/MM/DD'), ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)"

"SELECT " +" T_ODR.ODR_NO, " +" T_ODR.ODR_TYP, " +" T_ODR.CUST_ODR_NO, " +" T_ODR_CTL.CUST_ITEM_CD, " +" T_ODR_CTL.ITEM_CD, " +" TO_CHAR(T_ODR.DESINATED_DLV_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AS DESINATED_DLV_DATE, " +" T_ODR.ODR_QTY, " +" T_ODR.UNIT_CD, " +" T_ODR.ODR_UNIT_PRICE, " +" T_ODR.ODR_AMOUNT, " +" T_ODR.ODR_AMOUNT_EXCH_RATES, " +" T_ODR.DLV_LOC_CD, " +" T_ODR.DEPO_TYP, " +" TO_CHAR(T_ODR.ODR_ACPT_DATE,'YYYY/MM/DD') AS ODR_ACPT_DATE, " +" T_ODR.REMARKS, " +" T_ODR.CUST_CHRG_PSN_CD, " +" T_ODR.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" AS \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\", " +" USER_MST.USER_NAME, " +" T_ODR.CUST_CHRG_ORG_CD, " +" M_ORG.ORG_NAME " +"FROM " +" T_ODR, " +" T_ODR_CTL, " +" USER_MST, " +" M_ORG " +"WHERE " +" T_ODR.ODR_CTL_NO = T_ODR_CTL.ODR_CTL_NO " +" AND T_ODR.CUST_CHRG_PSN_CD = USER_MST.USER_CD(+) " +" AND T_ODR.CUST_CHRG_ORG_CD = M_ORG.ORG_CD(+) " +" AND T_ODR.ODR_CMPLT_FLG = 0 " +" AND T_ODR.DEL_FLG = 0 " +" AND T_ODR.ODR_TYP = 3 " +" AND T_ODR.TOTAL_SHIP_QTY = 0 " +" AND T_ODR.ODR_NO = ? " +" AND T_ODR_CTL.CUST_CD = ? " +" AND M_ORG.COMPANY_CD(+) = ?"
"UPDATE " +" T_ODR " +"SET " +" \\"JOB_ODR_SET_FLG\\" = ? " +"WHERE " +" T_ODR.\\"ODR_NO\\" = ?"

"INSERT INTO " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK(\\"ODR_NO\\", \\"COMPANY_CD\\", \\"SLIP_CD\\", \\"CUST_ODR_NO\\", \\"CUST_CD\\", \\"ITEM_CD\\", \\"ITEM_NAME\\", \\"CUST_CHRG_PSN_CD\\", \\"ODR_ACPT_PSN_CD\\", \\"CURRNCY_CD\\", \\"EXCH_TYP\\", \\"DESINATED_DLV_DATE\\", \\"ODR_UNIT_PRICE\\", \\"ODR_QTY\\", \\"ODR_AMOUNT\\", \\"ODR_AMOUNT_EXCH_RATES\\", \\"TAX_APPLY_TYP\\", \\"TAX_CD\\", \\"TAX_CALC_TYP\\", \\"REMARKS\\", \\"ODR_ACPT_DATE\\", \\"ORGN_ODR_NO\\", \\"ADD_ODR_FLG\\", \\"ODR_CMPLT_FLG\\", \\"ODR_CMPLT_DATE\\", \\"DEL_FLG\\", \\"CUST_CHRG_ORG_CD\\", \\"ODR_ACPT_ORG_CD\\") " +"VALUES " +" (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD'), ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD'), ?, ?, ?, TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD'), ?, ?, ?)"

"SELECT " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK.ODR_NO, " +" 3, " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK.CUST_ODR_NO, " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK.ITEM_CD, " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK.ITEM_CD, " +" TO_CHAR(T_ODR_UNSTOCK.DESINATED_DLV_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AS DESINATED_DLV_DATE, " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK.ODR_QTY, " +" B.STOCK_UNIT AS \\"UNIT_CD\\", " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK.ODR_UNIT_PRICE, " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK.ODR_AMOUNT, " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK.ODR_AMOUNT_EXCH_RATES, " +" '' AS \\"DLV_LOC_CD\\", " +" 10, " +" TO_CHAR(T_ODR_UNSTOCK.ODR_ACPT_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AS ODR_ACPT_DATE, " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK.REMARKS, " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK.CUST_CHRG_PSN_CD, " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" AS \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\", " +" A.USER_NAME, " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK.CUST_CHRG_ORG_CD AS \\"CUST_CHRG_ORG_CD\\", " +" C.ORG_NAME " +"FROM " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK, " +" ( " +" SELECT " +" USER_MST.USER_NAME, " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK.ODR_NO " +" FROM " +" USER_MST, " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK " +" WHERE " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK.CUST_CHRG_PSN_CD = USER_MST.USER_CD(+) " +" ) A, " +" ( " +" SELECT " +" M_ITEM.STOCK_UNIT, " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK.ODR_NO " +" FROM " +" M_ITEM, " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK " +" WHERE " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK.ITEM_CD = M_ITEM.ITEM_CD(+) " +" ) B, " +" ( " +" SELECT " +" M_ORG.ORG_NAME, " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK.ODR_NO " +" FROM " +" M_ORG, " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK " +" WHERE " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK.CUST_CHRG_ORG_CD = M_ORG.ORG_CD(+) " +" AND M_ORG.COMPANY_CD(+) = ? " +" ) C " +"WHERE " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK.ODR_NO = A.ODR_NO " +" AND T_ODR_UNSTOCK.ODR_NO = B.ODR_NO " +" AND T_ODR_UNSTOCK.ODR_NO = C.ODR_NO " +" AND T_ODR_UNSTOCK.ODR_CMPLT_FLG = 0 " +" AND T_ODR_UNSTOCK.DEL_FLG = 0 " +" AND T_ODR_UNSTOCK.ODR_NO = ?"

"UPDATE " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK " +"SET " +" \\"CUST_ODR_NO\\" = ?, " +" \\"ITEM_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"CUST_CHRG_PSN_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"DESINATED_DLV_DATE\\" = TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD'), " +" \\"REMARKS\\" = ?, " +" \\"CUST_CHRG_ORG_CD\\" = ? " +"WHERE " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK.\\"ODR_NO\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" T_ESTIMATE.\\"ESTIMATE_NO\\" AS \\"ESTIMATE_NO\\", " +" T_ESTIMATE.\\"ESTIMATE_STAT\\" AS \\"ESTIMATE_STAT\\", " +" T_ESTIMATE.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" AS \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\", " +" T_ESTIMATE.\\"ES_ORG_CD\\" AS \\"ES_ORG_CD\\", " +" T_ESTIMATE.\\"ES_USER_CD\\" AS \\"ES_USER_CD\\" " +"FROM " +" T_ESTIMATE " +"WHERE " +" T_ESTIMATE.\\"PROJECT_CD\\" = ? " +" AND T_ESTIMATE.\\"ESTIMATE_NO\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.\\"DETAL_NO\\" AS \\"DETAL_NO\\", " +" T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.\\"CUST_ITEM_CD\\" AS \\"CUST_ITEM_CD\\", " +" T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" AS \\"ITEM_NAME\\", " +" T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.\\"ESTIMATE_QTY\\" AS \\"ESTIMATE_QTY\\", " +" T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.\\"ESTIMATE_UNIT_PRICE\\" AS \\"ESTIMATE_UNIT_PRICE\\", " +" T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.\\"ESTIMATE_AMOUNT\\" AS \\"ESTIMATE_AMOUNT\\", " +" T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.\\"ESTIMATE_TYPE\\" AS \\"ESTIMATE_TYPE\\", " +" TO_CHAR(T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.\\"DESINATED_DLV_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') AS \\"DESINATED_DLV_DATE\\", " +" A.STOCK_UNIT AS \\"UNIT_CD\\" " +"FROM " +" T_ESTIMATE_DETAL, " +" ( " +" SELECT " +" M_ITEM.STOCK_UNIT, " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.CUST_CD, " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.CUST_ITEM_CD " +" FROM " +" M_ITEM, " +" M_ITEM_SPEC, " +" T_PROJECT " +" WHERE " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = '00' " +" AND M_ITEM_SPEC.ITEM_CD = M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\"(+) " +" AND M_ITEM_SPEC.\\"CUST_CD\\" = T_PROJECT.\\"CUST_CD\\" " +" AND T_PROJECT.\\"PROJECT_CD\\" = ? " +" ) A " +"WHERE " +" T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.\\"PROJECT_CD\\" = ? " +" AND T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.\\"ESTIMATE_NO\\" = ? " +" AND A.\\"CUST_ITEM_CD\\"(+) = T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.\\"CUST_ITEM_CD\\" " +"ORDER BY " +" T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.\\"DETAL_NO\\""

"UPDATE " +" T_ESTIMATE_DETAL " +"SET " +" \\"ODR_FLG\\" = ? " +"WHERE " +" T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.\\"PROJECT_CD\\" = ? " +" AND T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.\\"ESTIMATE_NO\\" = ? " +" AND T_ESTIMATE_DETAL.\\"DETAL_NO\\" = ?"

"SELECT " +" T_ESTIMATE.\\"ESTIMATE_NO\\" AS \\"ESTIMATE_NO\\", " +" T_ESTIMATE.\\"ESTIMATE_STAT\\" AS \\"ESTIMATE_STAT\\", " +" T_ESTIMATE.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" AS \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\", " +" T_ESTIMATE.\\"ES_ORG_CD\\" AS \\"ES_ORG_CD\\", " +" T_ESTIMATE.\\"ES_USER_CD\\" AS \\"ES_USER_CD\\" " +"FROM " +" T_ESTIMATE " +"WHERE " +" T_ESTIMATE.\\"PROJECT_CD\\" = ? " +" AND T_ESTIMATE.\\"ESTIMATE_NO\\" = ? " +"UNION " +"SELECT " +" T_ESTIMATE.\\"ESTIMATE_NO\\" AS \\"ESTIMATE_NO\\", " +" T_ESTIMATE.\\"ESTIMATE_STAT\\" AS \\"ESTIMATE_STAT\\", " +" T_ESTIMATE.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" AS \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\", " +" T_ESTIMATE.\\"ES_ORG_CD\\" AS \\"ES_ORG_CD\\", " +" T_ESTIMATE.\\"ES_USER_CD\\" AS \\"ES_USER_CD\\" " +"FROM " +" T_ESTIMATE " +"WHERE " +" T_ESTIMATE.\\"PROJECT_CD\\" = ? " +" AND T_ESTIMATE.\\"ESTIMATE_STAT\\" = 2"
"SELECT " +" A.JOB_ODR_CD " +"FROM " +" T_JOB_ODR A " +"WHERE " +" A.JOB_ODR_CD = ?"
"SELECT " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" AS \\"ITEM_CD\\" " +"FROM " +" M_ITEM " +"WHERE " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" AND(M_ITEM.\\"MRP_ODR_TYP\\" = 1 " +" OR M_ITEM.\\"MRP_ODR_TYP\\" = 2)"
"SELECT " +" M_CAL_H.CAL_NO " +"FROM " +" M_PLANT, " +" M_CAL_H " +"WHERE " +" M_PLANT.CAL_NO = M_CAL_H.CAL_NO " +" AND M_PLANT.PLANT_CD = ?"

"SELECT " +" M_CAL.HOLIDAY_FLG " +"FROM " +" M_PLANT, " +" M_CAL " +"WHERE " +" M_PLANT.PLANT_CD = ? " +" AND M_PLANT.CAL_NO = M_CAL.CAL_NO " +" AND M_CAL.CAL_DATE = TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD') " +" AND M_CAL.HOLIDAY_FLG = '1'"
"insert into " +" T_ODR_CTL(\\"ODR_CTL_NO\\", \\"CUST_CD\\", \\"CUST_ITEM_CD\\", \\"CUST_ITEM_NAME\\", \\"ITEM_CD\\", \\"ITEM_NAME\\", \\"DEL_FLG\\") " +"values " +" (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, 0)"

"SELECT " +" T_ODR_CTL.\\"ODR_CTL_NO\\" AS \\"ODR_CTL_NO\\" " +"FROM " +" T_ODR_CTL " +"WHERE " +" T_ODR_CTL.\\"CUST_CD\\" = ? " +" AND T_ODR_CTL.\\"CUST_ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" AND T_ODR_CTL.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" AND T_ODR_CTL.\\"DEL_FLG\\" = 0"
"SELECT " +" 'OCN' || LPAD(TO_CHAR(SEQ_ODR_CTL.NEXTVAL), 7, '0') AS \\"ODR_CTL_NO\\" " +"FROM " +" DUAL"
"SELECT " +" 'ODR' || LPAD(TO_CHAR(SEQ_ODR.NEXTVAL), 10, '0') AS \\"ODR_NO\\" " +"FROM " +" DUAL"

"INSERT INTO " +" T_ODR_ACPT_RSLT(\\"RSLT_CTL_SEQ_CD\\", \\"ODR_CTL_NO\\", \\"ODR_NO\\", \\"CUST_ODR_NO\\", \\"ODR_TYP\\", \\"CUST_CD\\", \\"CUST_ITEM_CD\\", \\"ITEM_CD\\", \\"DESINATED_DLV_DATE\\", \\"ODR_QTY\\", \\"UNIT\\", \\"DLV_PLACE_CD\\", \\"UNIT_PRICE\\", \\"CUR_CD\\", \\"SPCL_PRICE_CO\\", \\"DEPO_TYP\\", \\"CUST_DLV_CD\\", \\"CUST_DLV_KEY_CD\\", \\"REMARKS\\", \\"CUST_CHRG_PSN_CD\\", \\"ODR_ACPT_PSN_CD\\", \\"IF_CTL_NO\\", \\"ODR_SEQ\\", \\"ODR_ACPT_DATE\\", \\"TAX_CD\\") " +"VALUES " +" (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD'), ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD'), ?)"

"INSERT INTO " +" T_ANS_DLV_DATE(\\"ODR_NO\\", \\"PART_DLV_SEQ_NO\\", \\"LAST_ANS_DLV_DATE_RCD\\", \\"DESINATED_SHIP_DATE\\", \\"DESINATED_SHIP_QTY\\", \\"REST_SHIP_ODR_QTY\\", \\"SHIP_ODR_CMPLT_FLG\\", \\"IF_CTL_NO\\", \\"DEL_FLG\\") " +"VALUES " +" (?, ?, TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD'), TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD'), ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)"
"SELECT " +" T_ANS_DLV_DATE.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" AS \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" " +"FROM " +" T_ANS_DLV_DATE " +"WHERE " +" T_ANS_DLV_DATE.\\"ODR_NO\\" = ? " +" AND T_ANS_DLV_DATE.\\"DEL_FLG\\" = 0"

"INSERT INTO " +" T_JOB_ODR(\\"JOB_ODR_CD\\", \\"JOB_ODR_CANCEL_NO\\", \\"JOB_ODR_TYP\\", \\"ITEM_CD\\", \\"PLAN_TYP\\", \\"JOB_ODR_DLV_DATE\\", \\"JOB_ODR_QTY\\", \\"ALC_GRP_CD\\", \\"JOB_ODR_STS_TYP\\", \\"JOB_ODR_EXP_TYP\\", \\"JOB_ODR_DEL_FLG\\", \\"PLANT_CD\\") " +"VALUES " +" (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, TO_DATE(?,'YYYY/MM/DD'), ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)"
"INSERT INTO " +" SYS_JOB_OD_CALC_CTRL(PLANT_CD, JOB_ODR_CD, OD_CALC_FLG, OD_MNT_FLG) " +"VALUES " +" (?, ?, 0, 1)"
